#赏花刷屏&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Bright orange lilies bloom amidst green leaves, surrounded by gray rocks. A decorative metal piece with spirals is partially visible in the background near a concrete border." height="6048" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/itsbrian/6a052b2a51f61.jpg" width="8064"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://itsbrian.some.pics"&gt;@itsbrian&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 01:53:55 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a051fa1433a0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;爱上了我的最新#纹身——为我的祖母Althea制作的#纪念。图案包括一只#壁虎，周围环绕着Althaea#花朵的花瓣，并配有文字“Spiritus Altheae”🌸 由洛杉矶的Nikola Ivana设计并完成，她太棒了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A detailed tattoo on a person's foot and ankle. The tattoo features a vibrant green gecko with orange spots and blue-tinted feet, positioned as if it is crawling downward toward the toes. Pink hibiscus-like flowers and green leaves are artfully intertwined around the gecko's body. To the right of the gecko's curved tail, the words &amp;quot;SPIRITUS ALTHEAE&amp;quot; are tattooed in a clean, sans-serif capitalized font. The entire piece is set against a background of warm-toned wood flooring." height="3768" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/6a051fa1433a0.jpg" width="3040"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 01:04:37 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>囤积癖的困扰</title><link>https://some.pics/6a04d2434e737</link><description>&lt;p&gt;囤积者&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Closeup of an old Dell Optiplex Micro computer front pane." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a04d2434e737.jpg" width="1125"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 19:34:29 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>